      <abstract label="Abstract">Correspondence, autobiography, reports, memoranda, military orders, citations, and
printed matter, relating primarily to the operation of the U.S. Signal Corps, especially
during World War II. Includes three Italian government documents relating to Benito
Mussolini.</abstract>
      <langmaterial label="Language">
        <language langcode="eng">English.</language>
      </langmaterial>
    </did>
